    public interface NeighbourSelection<V extends Variable<V,T>,T extends Value<V,T>>
    Neighbour selection criterion.

    In each iteration of the solver, a neighbour is selected and assigned (by default StandardNeighbourSelection is employed).
    Version:
    IFS 1.3 (Iterative Forward Search)
